                          History of gdbase
                          -----------------

9/1998 (V 2.1c)  -corrections and additions by Markus Neteler
                                 <neteler@geog.uni-hannover.de>
   - gawk error in gdbase/gdbase.cmd:
           - changed /%s/ to \"%s\" due to errors in "<" and ">" comparisons
           - added ~ to ! command: !~ instead of ! due to errors with
             "not" command
   - corrected gdbase/gdb.display:
      orig:
        dig) v.reclass -d type=area input=$INPUT output=$OUTPUT.a  < /tmp/v.reclass.$$;
      corrected:
        dig) v.reclass -d type=area input=$INPUT output=$OUTPUT.a  < /tmp/reclass.$$;


8/1998 (V 2.1b)
  -corrections by Bozena Friedrich <b.friedrich@agrar.hu-berlin.de>
      to query.tk 
        -scroll  -> xscroll
         view    -> xview

  -corrections and additions by Markus Neteler
     - d.erase button in display mode
     - gawk error in gdbase/gdbase.cmd:
           - (newrule="") eliminated
     - Gmakefile added 


